<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="light">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>STAC API - Geokuup</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@4.12.14/dist/full.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-white to-green-50">
        <div class="navbar bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
            <div class="flex-1">
                <a href="/stac/web/" class="btn btn-ghost text-xl">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    STAC API
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-none">
                <ul class="menu menu-horizontal px-1">
                    <li><a href="/stac/web/browse" class="btn btn-ghost">Browse</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/stac/web/search" class="btn btn-ghost">Search</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/stac/api/v1/docs" class="btn btn-ghost">API Docs</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero min-h-[60vh] bg-base-200">
            <div class="hero-content text-center">
                <div class="max-w-4xl">
                    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
                        <span class="text-primary">STAC</span> API
                    </h1>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">SpatioTemporal Asset Catalog</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        Welcome to the Geokuup STAC API - a modern geospatial data catalog implementing the 
                        <a href="https://stacspec.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link link-primary">STAC specification</a>. 
                        Discover, browse, and access geospatial datasets with standardized metadata and intuitive interfaces.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
                        <a href="/stac/web/browse" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 7v10a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-6l-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2z" />
                            </svg>
                            Browse Data
                        </a>
                        <a href="/stac/web/search" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
                            </svg>
                            Search Items
                        </a>
                        <a href="/stac/api/v1/" class="btn btn-accent btn-lg">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
                            </svg>
                            API Root
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About STAC</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <p>
                            The <strong>SpatioTemporal Asset Catalog (STAC)</strong> specification provides a common 
                            language to describe geospatial information, making it easier to index and discover data.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            STAC is a standardized way to expose collections of spatial temporal data. It enables 
                            interoperability between geospatial data providers and consumers through a common metadata structure.
                        </p>
                        <div class="alert alert-info">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="stroke-current shrink-0 w-6 h-6">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <span>
                                This API implements <strong>STAC API v1.0.0</strong> with support for Core, Collections, 
                                and Features conformance classes.
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Quick Links</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="card bg-base-200">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h3 class="card-title text-lg">API Endpoints</h3>
                                <ul class="space-y-2">
                                    <li>
                                        <a href="/stac/api/v1/" class="link link-primary">
                                            /stac/api/v1/ - API Landing Page
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <a href="/stac/api/v1/collections" class="link link-primary">
                                            /stac/api/v1/collections - Collections List
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <a href="/stac/api/v1/search" class="link link-primary">
                                            /stac/api/v1/search - Search Endpoint
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <a href="/stac/api/v1/docs" class="link link-primary">
                                            /stac/api/v1/docs - API Documentation
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card bg-base-200">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h3 class="card-title text-lg">Web Interfaces</h3>
                                <ul class="space-y-2">
                                    <li>
                                        <a href="/stac/web/browse" class="link link-secondary">
                                            /stac/web/browse - Data Browser
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <a href="/stac/web/search" class="link link-secondary">
                                            /stac/web/search - Search Interface
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-secondary/10">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title text-2xl">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
                            </svg>
                            Geokuup Portal
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mb-4">
                            Explore more geospatial services and applications through the Geokuup portal - 
                            a comprehensive platform for spatial data infrastructure and environmental monitoring.
                        </p>
                        <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                            <a href="https://geokuup.ee" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">
                                Visit Geokuup
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
                                </svg>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-info/10">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title text-2xl">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                            </svg>
                            Contact & Support
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mb-4">
                            This STAC API is maintained by the Landscape Geoinformatics research group at 
                            the University of Tartu. For questions, support, or collaboration opportunities, 
                            please visit our website.
                        </p>
                        <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                            <a href="https://landscape-geoinformatics.ut.ee" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-accent">
                                Visit Our Lab
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
                                </svg>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer class="footer footer-center p-10 bg-base-200 text-base-content rounded mt-16">
            <nav class="grid grid-flow-col gap-4">
                <a href="/stac/web/browse" class="link link-hover">Browse</a>
                <a href="/stac/web/search" class="link link-hover">Search</a>
                <a href="/stac/api/v1/" class="link link-hover">API</a>
                <a href="/stac/api/v1/docs" class="link link-hover">Documentation</a>
            </nav>
            <nav>
                <div class="grid grid-flow-col gap-4">
                    <a href="https://landscape-geoinformatics.ut.ee" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link link-hover">Landscape Geoinformatics Lab</a>
                    <a href="https://geokuup.ee" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link link-hover">Geokuup Portal</a>
                    <a href="https://stacspec.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link link-hover">STAC Specification</a>
                </div>
            </nav>
            <aside>
                <p>Copyright © 2024 - Geokuup STAC API | University of Tartu</p>
            </aside>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
